<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَفْرَادُ الْعَلَمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٦٩ - وَالْبَرْذَعِيْ صَنَّفَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَفْرَادَ الْعَلَمْ»</span> … أَسْمَاءً اوْ أَلْقَاباً اوْ كُنىً تُضَمّْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٧٠ - كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَجْمَدٍ»</span>، وَكَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«جُبَيْبٍ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَنْدَرِ»</span> … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«شَكَلٍ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«صُنَابِحِ بْنِ الْأَعْسَرِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٧١ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَبِي مُعَيْدٍ»</span>، وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَبِي الْمُدِلَّهْ»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَبِي مُرَايَةَ»</span> اسْمُهُ: عَبْدُ اللَّهْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٧٧٢ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَفِينَةٍ»</span> مِهْرَانَ، ثُمَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مِنْدَلِ»</span> … بِالْكَسْرِ فِي الْمِيمِ؛ وَفَتْحُهَا جَلِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>• • •<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>